Well, I´d say that in any of those situation (ie: when u need to cross thru a KOS town) your lvl 8 spell Gather Shadows works just fine since it lasts long enough to pass across that dangerous spot.<BR>
Can anyone else state whether I´m wrong or not? Is there any other alternative use of this Gather Shadows effect. Cause, honestly, I´m not paying that use amounts of money just to save a spell slot in a very certain moment, no matter if its a-while-running-no-casting-time effect.<BR>
